28
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:52,960
And anyway, this philanthropist said, well,

29
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:58,000
let's have a conference to discuss that.

30
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:00,960
And if we can find some serious problem

31
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:06,440
that nobody has noticed, and so on and so forth.

32
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:09,000
So what do you think?

33
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:14,800
Now, during the period when AI looked

34
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:19,360
