35
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:24,000
got panicked and went into science fiction mode

36
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:32,000
and said, well, what if the two novels I found very impressive,

37
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:37,960
one was Colossus by an English writer named D.F. Jones.

38
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:41,000
Any of you read that?

39
